{"tid":2274151,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺專做淡倉既都係反社會人格？心理唔平衡痴線佬居多？","createTime":"2020-11-06T08:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T13:02:06.000Z","uid":16063,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1481c33d8fb1fe873fdfbd7e006754311b724a59","tid":2274151,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"玩正股 Call Side = 睇好間公司 = 想股價升 <br />\n間公司發展得好 = 人類科技進步 = 最後benefit到自己<br />\n或者望社會經濟好 = 龍市 = 升<br />\n好友望社會又繼續向未來發展 <br />\n大家又有錢齊齊賺 皆大歡喜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但淡友日日望跌 佢地自私自利 <br />\n想係自己贏錢既時候 仲可以睇住人地輸錢<br />\n佢地寧願經濟唔好係熊市 / 科技公司無突破人類文明停滯 <br />\n都想好友仆街得自己贏錢<br />\n<br />\n所以各位龍友望到淡友應該日日指住佢地嚟屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌到班自私撚懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ccfb6091d6464897ed11c183a267094e06cb0d","tid":2274151,"uid":357040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"覺！"},{"pid":"49712c942a759a7587245bfa2de80c046e31ec75","tid":2274151,"uid":131884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"所以今年咪玩撚死班仆街"},{"pid":"224bbdc6653bd91bde941fb51e3ca2ac2d89cc8b","tid":2274151,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ccfb6091d6464897ed11c183a267094e06cb0d","tid":2274151,"uid":357040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"覺！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"龍軍一齊指撚住班淡友屌死佢‼️‼️<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3a7def73da34fe8981c962bd4051f67af52996","tid":2274151,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49712c942a759a7587245bfa2de80c046e31ec75","tid":2274151,"uid":131884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:50:33.000Z","m